{"tid":1448011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真心戰術討論","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:38.000Z","uid":41963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"168ba4e70c77b283b0c6a3ed40620dee92142525","tid":1448011,"uid":41963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意: 唔駛驚今晚大把彈藥，只係睇大家利用成點<br />\n<br />\n政治局勢: 9月9日美國國會復會 (即係香港9月10)，10月1共匪竊國日。<br />\n<br />\n前線局勢: 黑犬新戰術(輕裝伏擊)+武警增援。滲透各個戰區，引人去有利佢地既地形然後一網打盡，就算引唔走，都不停擾亂現場討論導致遲遲未有共識，降低現場手足既行動力。<br />\n<br />\n網上局勢: 連登同TG都極多風向網軍，在家既手足又係想幫都好難作出行動。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n個人見解<br />\n戰略上: 手足一定要喺上面提到既兩個時間點做最多既野，一直堅持直到五大訴求都得到回應。<br />\n<br />\n戰術上: 拋得開道德底線就麻包袋，拋唔開就連環三罷。<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益。"},{"pid":"b446e8e254900217b69432d0464d3c51687af92d","tid":1448011,"uid":41963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da7340fd02c8deca1f586bdbf2676c07d7affb8","tid":1448011,"uid":41963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d12667f02fa8e25e38e6c61336c48c07eb8ba32","tid":1448011,"uid":41963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c58d948c29b0f34cf2f2ab039e18b7996424e4","tid":1448011,"uid":41963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:18.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"4706cef67d118b52c254994239a69169788f949b","tid":1448011,"uid":43413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:49.000Z","msg":"戰術係有<br />\n<br />\n1.打狗<br />\n2.救人<br />\n<br />\n前題係無共識<br />\n<br />\n兩樣野都係掛住走係做唔到"},{"pid":"78deee291be5bf33167ae56d13eabb4bfaeb46e1","tid":1448011,"uid":4196